race.description: Greg Martlew Autos Stake Pr1 Division1
race.comment: PATRIOT MILLARD (1) is on a hot streak recording a 17.55 win over 305m at this track last start following on from a speedy 22.21 success at Warrnambool over 390m the start prior. Hard to top on recent times. ONE MORE BUTTON (5) turned in a moderate effort last time when eighth at Warrnambool over 450m behind Layla Nova (26.61) in a Grade 5. Was in the money prior to that. Strong form has emerged from his last run. Can figure in the finish. ASTON GLEAM (2) turned in a modest effort most recently when seventh at this track over 400m behind Mister Cadillac (23.74) in a OPEN. Scored at his previous run. Will give the top chances plenty to think about. ENERGY TO BURN (7) was strongly fancied last time but finished second (17.61), beaten 1.3 lengths. Form from his last run is proving to be solid. Overdue and expected to feature again.
